metadata.name: #1 Zerk Pass
metadata.description:
Zerk Pass is a 333 genesis collection. Owning a Zerk Pass will give you exclusive access to NFT alpha provided by NFTZerk and his team, WL Giveaways and raffles, exclusive NFT trading tools and much more. 

To gain access to these perks, you must own 1 NFT and verify your ownership within the Zerk Pass Discord, you will then have full access to all exclusive channels. To find out more on what this pass includes please visit the Zerk Pass twitter and website.
